          "correctAnswer": 0,
          "explanations": {
            "A": "Correct. Standard Bernoulli variance formula.",
            "B": "p² is not the variance of a Bernoulli trial.",
            "C": "1 − p is the failure probability, not variance.",
            "D": "p is the mean, not the variance."
